<p class="has-tablet-text-align-justify has-mobile-text-align-justify">In conclusion, the VTU CGPA Calculator serves as a accurate tool for engineering students. It saves time of calculating for long hours. You can also use SGPA calculator like this without any problem. The user interface is designed in such a way that everyone can easily get the precise output.</p>
